since you don't remember.

21
00:01:46,430 --> 00:01:48,470
Goodness, it's all done.

22
00:01:57,560 --> 00:01:58,440
Hello?

23
00:01:59,820 --> 00:02:01,110
Yes, it is.

24
00:02:11,410 --> 00:02:14,250
