31
00:02:36,770 --> 00:02:38,400
Why did I do that?

32
00:02:40,690 --> 00:02:43,690
If only I changed his name...

33
00:02:45,900 --> 00:02:47,030
I feel like

34
00:02:48,320 --> 00:02:50,080
it's my fault.

35
00:02:53,660 --> 00:02:56,000
Everyday I want to turn back time

36
00:02:57,420 --> 00:03:00,130
to that day tens of thousands of times.

37
00:03:02,750 --> 00:03:04,880
If only I stopped her

38
00:03:05,880 --> 00:03:08,470
from going to work

39
00:03:10,430 --> 00:03:11,720
just for five minutes.

40
00:03:12,140 --> 00:03:13,220
No,

41
00:03:15,480 --> 00:03:18,060
just for one more minute,

42
00:03:19,060 --> 00:03:21,110
