43
00:03:24,530 --> 00:03:26,700
Why didn't I stop her?

44
00:03:38,040 --> 00:03:40,460
But even if there is a blinker,

45
00:03:41,040 --> 00:03:45,510
bad luck will never turn it on
so we can notice it.

46
00:03:46,420 --> 00:03:48,090
She died because of me.

47
00:03:51,300 --> 00:03:53,760
I killed her.

48
00:03:55,310 --> 00:03:56,230
I did.

49
00:03:58,480 --> 00:04:00,310
I killed her.

50
00:04:05,030 --> 00:04:06,150
Bring Yu-ri back.

51
00:04:07,190 --> 00:04:08,780
Bring her back.

52
00:04:10,160 --> 00:04:12,740
Bring her back, you jerk.

53
00:04:13,740 --> 00:04:15,160
Bring Yu-ri back.

54
00:04:16,040 --> 00:04:18,210
So you don't have to blame yourself

55
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:20,540
for not seeing it.

56
00:04:21,040 --> 00:04:25,960
EPISODE 14: IT'S NOT YOUR FAULT

57
00:04:28,420 --> 00:04:29,470
Min-jeong.

58
00:04:31,300 --> 00:04:33,350
Why are you crying? Don't cry.

59
00:04:33,850 --> 00:04:36,100
It's not your fault. Okay?

60
00:04:38,680 --> 00:04:40,520
Then whose fault is it?

61
00:04:43,110 --> 00:04:45,440
Is it because you're at the hospital
all day long?

62
00:04:48,490 --> 00:04:52,320
