65
00:05:03,830 --> 00:05:06,300
If all of those aren't my fault,
whose fault is it?

66
00:05:08,460 --> 00:05:09,550
Am I not her mother?

67
00:05:10,130 --> 00:05:11,090
Min-jeong.

68
00:05:12,380 --> 00:05:16,560
