72
00:05:34,200 --> 00:05:35,280
I'm sorry.

73
00:05:36,910 --> 00:05:37,950
I'm sorry.

74
00:05:41,750 --> 00:05:43,580
Why are you always

75
00:05:45,330 --> 00:05:46,630
sorry

76
