I can truly be Seo-woo's mom.

84
00:07:06,830 --> 00:07:07,870
The pick-up helper.

85
00:07:14,840 --> 00:07:15,800
That's her.

86
00:07:16,800 --> 00:07:17,800
Yu-ri.

87
00:07:19,640 --> 00:07:20,510
Cha Yu-ri.

88
00:07:34,820 --> 00:07:35,900
What

89
00:07:37,950 --> 00:07:38,950
do you...

90
00:07:41,320 --> 00:07:42,780
What do you mean?

91
00:07:49,080 --> 00:07:50,580
Seo-woo's biological mother.

92
00:07:52,420 --> 00:07:53,500
Cha Yu-ri.

93
00:07:57,550 --> 00:07:58,970
