97
00:09:49,450 --> 00:09:50,540
Seo-woo, you're up.

98
00:09:54,960 --> 00:09:57,090
Seo-woo, good morning.
Shall we wash your face?

99
00:10:01,010 --> 00:10:02,220
Min-jeong.

100
00:10:18,480 --> 00:10:19,860
All done.

101
00:10:28,950 --> 00:10:29,950
Okay.

102
00:10:41,710 --> 00:10:43,380
Stay here for a minute.

103
00:11:07,200 --> 00:11:09,370
Won't you get ready for work? You're late.

104
00:11:11,240 --> 00:11:12,950
I know you can't believe it.

105
00:11:15,540 --> 00:11:17,170
Because I couldn't either.

106
00:11:20,170 --> 00:11:22,550
No, I don't believe it.

107
00:11:23,840 --> 00:11:25,380
It doesn't make sense.

108
00:11:26,220 --> 00:11:27,800
Does this make sense to you?

109
00:11:28,430 --> 00:11:29,840
The kitchen assistant.

110
00:11:30,510 --> 00:11:33,180
The pick-up helper is Seo-woo's mom?

111
00:11:33,560 --> 00:11:34,930
She came back to life?

112
00:11:36,270 --> 00:11:37,390
Stop joking around.

113
00:11:37,480 --> 00:11:40,310
Why would I make a joke like this?

114
00:11:40,810 --> 00:11:43,860
Exactly. Why would someone
joke around like this?

115
00:11:45,900 --> 00:11:48,950
This is the worst you've ever been.

116
00:11:52,330 --> 00:11:53,620
It's unbelievable,

117
00:11:55,080 --> 00:11:56,000
