Fine.

121
00:12:12,100 --> 00:12:14,260
Let's say what you're saying is true.

122
00:12:16,020 --> 00:12:17,270
Then

123
00:12:20,190 --> 00:12:21,650
why did you tell me this

124
00:12:22,360 --> 00:12:23,480
now?

125
00:12:29,820 --> 00:12:31,070
I'm sorry.

126
00:12:35,410 --> 00:12:37,410
At first, I was flustered,

127
00:12:38,500 --> 00:12:41,040
so I couldn't tell you.

128
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:44,710
But you can't be the only one
who doesn't know.

129
00:12:46,210 --> 00:12:47,300
Min-jeong.

130
00:12:47,800 --> 00:12:49,470
Believe it or not,

131
00:12:51,970 --> 00:12:53,140
it's true.

132
00:12:59,810 --> 00:13:01,520
MISAENG

133
00:13:07,980 --> 00:13:09,780
-Excuse me.
-Gosh.

134
00:13:10,320 --> 00:13:12,030
What's up with him?

135
00:13:12,110 --> 00:13:13,740
Why are you following me?

136
00:13:14,950 --> 00:13:16,410
Can you see me?

137
00:13:16,990 --> 00:13:18,410
Do you see ghosts, too?

138
00:13:18,500 --> 00:13:19,620
Can you see me?

139
00:13:21,660 --> 00:13:23,330
Are you on my left or right?

140
00:13:24,000 --> 00:13:26,000
-Where are you?
-Gosh.

141
00:13:26,090 --> 00:13:27,050
Darn.

142
00:13:28,130 --> 00:13:31,010
No, I'm a Christian.

143
00:13:31,090 --> 00:13:33,890
I don't believe in ghosts.

144
00:13:34,470 --> 00:13:36,970
I think I believe it a little.

145
00:13:37,640 --> 00:13:38,640
I did.

146
00:13:38,720 --> 00:13:40,480
It's because I go to fortunetellers.

147
00:13:40,560 --> 00:13:43,060
Why did Yu-ri tell me that?

148
00:13:43,140 --> 00:13:45,770
Gosh, he's no fun.

149
00:13:50,400 --> 00:13:51,780
Hyeon-jeong.

150
00:13:55,490 --> 00:13:56,530
Hyeon-jeong.

151
00:14:01,040 --> 00:14:02,290
Hyeon-jeong!

152
00:14:02,370 --> 00:14:03,460
Yes. What?

153
00:14:04,250 --> 00:14:05,920
How spicy do you want that to be?

154
00:14:06,000 --> 00:14:07,750
Goodness.

155
00:14:09,380 --> 00:14:11,340
-What is it this time?
-Oh, gosh.

156
00:14:12,300 --> 00:14:13,590
Is it because of Yu-ri?

157
00:14:19,430 --> 00:14:21,220
Why are you sighing
while talking about Yu-ri?

158
00:14:21,310 --> 00:14:22,390
What?

159
00:14:23,270 --> 00:14:25,690
You're the one who always sighs
because of her.

160
00:14:27,020 --> 00:14:30,020
I'm just worried about her,
and I feel bad for her.

161
00:14:30,780 --> 00:14:31,900
That's all.

162
00:14:32,400 --> 00:14:34,240
Yu-ri is Seo-woo's mom,

163
00:14:34,400 --> 00:14:37,370
so I want to help her,
but it's complicated.

164
00:14:38,370 --> 00:14:40,410
That's why I keep sighing.

165
00:14:40,990 --> 00:14:43,040
Gang-hwa and you feel the same way, too.

166
00:14:44,500 --> 00:14:45,670
I understand

167
00:14:47,330 --> 00:14:48,960
why Yu-ri hid from us

168
00:14:50,800 --> 00:14:52,710
instead of coming to us first.

169
00:14:54,050 --> 00:14:55,090
Why?

170
00:14:55,380 --> 00:14:57,640
Everyone is having a hard time
because I came back.

171
00:14:57,720 --> 00:15:01,220
Because of me, Gang-hwa and you
are such in pain.

172
00:15:02,270 --> 00:15:03,850
I shouldn't have gotten caught.

173
00:15:06,230 --> 00:15:08,100
What is it?

174
00:15:08,190 --> 00:15:09,610
Hey.

175
00:15:12,730 --> 00:15:14,820
-Watch the shop for me.
-Why?

176
00:15:14,900 --> 00:15:16,200
Where are you going?

177
00:15:16,320 --> 00:15:17,860
Hyeon-jeong, don't go.

178
00:15:17,950 --> 00:15:20,410
I can't look after the store alone
right now.

179
00:15:20,780 --> 00:15:22,450
I'm in a state of great fear.

180
00:15:23,160 --> 00:15:24,250
Hyeon-jeong!

181
00:15:27,170 --> 00:15:28,880
Are you out of your mind?

182
00:15:28,960 --> 00:15:30,670
How can you take your eyes off her?

183
00:15:30,750 --> 00:15:33,960
She was right behind me.

184
00:15:34,130 --> 00:15:36,840
It was just for a second.

185
00:15:36,930 --> 00:15:38,430
A split second.

186
00:15:40,180 --> 00:15:44,140
I knew something was strange last night.

187
00:15:44,720 --> 00:15:46,480
Did Gang-hwa's wife say something?

188
00:15:46,560 --> 00:15:49,940
Why wouldn't she
when the pick-up helper lost her kid?

189
00:15:52,650 --> 00:15:55,030
Gosh, you idiot!

190
00:15:55,110 --> 00:15:57,990
Idiot!

191
00:15:59,530 --> 00:16:01,570
-Gosh.
-Goodness.

192
00:16:04,660 --> 00:16:07,750
OH MIN-JEONG
I'M SORRY

