so it's about time they left.

209
00:17:10,770 --> 00:17:12,100
They held out a long time.

210
00:17:14,610 --> 00:17:15,770
I don't believe it.

211
00:17:18,860 --> 00:17:19,860
Well...

212
00:17:20,530 --> 00:17:22,110
They were taken

213
00:17:22,700 --> 00:17:23,990
