218
00:17:35,920 --> 00:17:38,590
Thank them when you get there.

219
00:17:43,300 --> 00:17:46,350
I should cook for Pil-seung one more time.

220
00:17:47,890 --> 00:17:49,180
Like you got enough time.

221
00:17:49,890 --> 00:17:51,770
Don't worry about others.

222
00:17:51,850 --> 00:17:53,850
Enjoy what you can while you're here.

223
00:17:53,940 --> 00:17:55,560
You idiot.

224
00:18:00,650 --> 00:18:03,200
I can't believe
what Pil-seung's family did.

225
00:18:03,990 --> 00:18:05,160
I'm so grateful.

226
00:18:07,370 --> 00:18:10,620
But I can't thank them
because they're gone.

227
00:18:12,830 --> 00:18:14,790
-Yu-ri.
-Yes, Mom?

228
00:18:15,080 --> 00:18:17,210
Come out. Hyeon-jeong is here.

229
00:18:17,920 --> 00:18:19,630
Really?

230
00:18:20,420 --> 00:18:21,300
What is it?

231
00:18:21,380 --> 00:18:22,840
Hyeon-jeong is here.

232
00:18:22,920 --> 00:18:24,380
Okay.

233
00:18:35,480 --> 00:18:36,480
Hey.

234
00:18:36,560 --> 00:18:38,310
What is this?

235
00:18:39,190 --> 00:18:40,940
Hey, hop in.

236
00:18:42,860 --> 00:18:43,950
Hyeon-jeong.

237
00:18:44,360 --> 00:18:46,200
What's all this? Where did you get it?

238
00:18:46,280 --> 00:18:48,570
Why do you even ask? I'm a hip like this.

239
00:18:48,660 --> 00:18:49,830
Get in.

240
00:18:50,660 --> 00:18:52,450
-Is it really okay?
-Sure.

241
00:18:53,040 --> 00:18:55,370
Yeon-ji. Bring your sister's bag.

242
00:18:57,920 --> 00:18:58,750
My gosh.

243
00:19:02,420 --> 00:19:03,920
