246
00:19:19,110 --> 00:19:20,270
Anywhere.

247
00:19:20,610 --> 00:19:22,110
We can go anywhere you want.

248
00:19:26,490 --> 00:19:28,200
Now she smiles.

249
00:19:28,780 --> 00:19:31,870
Gosh, I can tell they are soul mates.

250
00:19:34,120 --> 00:19:36,830
Mom, I think Hyeon-jeong
is the best. Right?

251
00:19:55,310 --> 00:19:57,310
-Yu-ri, do you like it?
-I love it.

252
00:19:57,940 --> 00:19:59,980
