263
00:20:25,250 --> 00:20:26,550
I'm okay.

264
00:20:26,800 --> 00:20:28,130
-Of course, I am.
-Hyeon-jeong.

265
00:20:29,720 --> 00:20:32,680
Gosh, no. This isn't right.

266
00:20:32,760 --> 00:20:35,430
No!

267
00:20:36,680 --> 00:20:38,020
Yu-ri.

268
00:20:38,480 --> 00:20:39,940
Hyeon-jeong.

269
00:21:02,460 --> 00:21:04,090
I love the scenery.

270
00:21:18,890 --> 00:21:20,180
Hyeon-jeong, hurry.

271
00:21:58,180 --> 00:21:59,470
Is this for me?

272
